Re: explanation for 徹底
by furrykef » Tue 09.06.2011 9:05 pm Hyperworm wrote:Incidentally, what's going on with the verb at the end of the OP's sentence...? >_>;Maybe it's actually a contraction of 作らないのだ? (or actually 作らぬのだ, but same meaning)
